title: fanoutqa: Who are the top 5 US athletes with the most Olympic medals and in what years were they born? (7ae1b4fff7374d6d)

chat_history.content: Who are the top 5 US athletes with the most Olympic medals and in what years were they born?

Here are the top five US athletes with the most Olympic medals:

1. Michael Phelps (Born 1985)
2. Mark Spitz (Born 1950)
3. Carl Lewis (Born 1961)
4. Jenny Thompson (Born 1973)
5. Dara Torres (Born 1967)

Michael Phelps is the most decorated Olympian of all time, with 28 medals, 23 of which are gold, in swimming events.
